# Test-fixture residue from CliEvidenceCommandTests (six `{Type}Tests_{Guid:N}.cs`
# patterns written into the FixtureEvidence test project root and deleted in
# `finally`). Orphans when the test process is killed mid-run. Committed
# fixture tests live in `Tests/` subdirs, so this top-level glob is safe.
IoCTools.Tools.Cli.Tests/TestProjects/FixtureEvidence.TestsProject/*Tests_*.cs
